--- Soundwave ---

Soundwave nods, internally resenting the menial task. He opens a 
commlink to Slugslinger, and any others still in the field that are 
participating in the DED operation, "This is Communications Officer 
Soundwave. All DED members are to report to the DED ship 
immediately, and prepare for launch. Sounwave out." Soundwave 
closes the commlink, and faces the Council Member who was 
present with contempt, "As I was saying before, where is the 
location to the ship?" He finishes with typical Soundwave 
politeness.
